{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775826382043,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d777e0f8c001E9VhkEctLfhx92","messageID":"msg_d777de45c001uD4PMX2Jhkg3gy","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_b5aed7bcc18945e3bf0a6027","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project structure to understand:\n1. The overall project layout and directory structure\n2. Any existing router-related code in pkg/router\n3. Existing design documents or architecture files\n4. The project's Go module structure and dependencies\n5. Any existing HTTP proxy or reverse proxy implementations\n\nSearch thoroughly in the working directory /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z and any related agentcube directories.\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- Project structure overview\n- Existing router code (if any)\n- Design document patterns/conventions used\n- Key dependencies and frameworks\n- Any relevant configuration files","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_28881dddcffeA8I1354cK4hdIt (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the complete summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive AgentCube Project Analysis\n\n### 1. Project Structure Overview\n\n```\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/\n├── go.mod                              # Go module: github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n├── go.sum                              # Dependency lock file\n├── project.md                          # Project context document\n├── design.md                           # AR-003: CRD shared types design\n├── proposal.md                         # AR-009: Router HTTP reverse proxy proposal\n├── delta-spec.md                       # AR-009: Detailed delta specification (821 lines)\n├── test_spec.md                        # TDD specification\n├── .sdd_prompt.md                      # SDD prompt with client-go reference docs\n├── coverage.out                        # Test coverage output\n│\n├── pkg/                                # Go packages (library code)\n│   ├── apis/runtime/v1alpha1/          # Kubernetes CRD type definitions\n│   │   ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD\n│   │   ├── codeinterpreter_types.go    # CodeInterpreter CRD\n│   │   ├── shared_types.go             # Shared types (TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType)\n│   │   ├── constants.go                # Shared constants\n│   │   ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n│   │   ├── doc.go                      # Package doc + code generation markers\n│   │   └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go    # Auto-generated DeepCopy methods\n│   └── workloadmanager/                # Workload Manager service\n│       ├── handler/                    # HTTP handlers\n│       │   ├── sandbox_lifecycle.go    # Lifecycle management (GC, TTL, idle cleanup)\n│       │   ├── sandbox_create.go       # Sandbox creation handler\n│       │   ├── sandbox_delete.go       # Sandbox deletion handler\n│       │   ├── constants.go            # GVRs, kinds, labels, annotations constants\n│       │   └── models.go              # Request/response models, SandboxInfo, EntryPoint\n│       ├── reconciler/                 # Kubernetes controller reconciler\n│       │   ├── reconciler.go           # SandboxReconciler with Informer + workqueue\n│       │   ├── agentruntime.go         # AgentRuntime event handlers\n│       │   ├── codeinterpreter.go      # CodeInterpreter event handlers\n│       │   ├── pod.go                  # Pod event handlers\n│       │   ├── sync.go                 # Sync logic\n│       │   ├── types.go               # Types and interfaces\n│       │   ├── event_handlers.go       # Event handler registration\n│       │   ├── metrics.go             # Prometheus metrics\n│       │   └── metrics_test.go        # Metrics tests\n│       └── response/                   # HTTP response helpers\n│           ├── response.go             # JSON, Created, Error, ErrorWithID helpers\n│           └── response_test.go\n│\n├── client-go/                          # Generated Kubernetes client code\n│   ├── clientset/                      # Typed clientset\n│   │   ├── clientset.go               # Clientset, Interface, constructors\n│   │   └── typed/runtime/v1alpha1/    # Typed REST clients for AR and CI\n│   ├── informers/externalversions/     # SharedInformerFactory\n│   │   ├── factory.go                 # Factory with Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync\n│   │   └── runtime/v1alpha1/          # Per-type informers (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n│   └── listers/runtime/v1alpha1/       # Lister interfaces (read-only cache)\n│\n├── changes/                            # Change request directories (AR-001 through AR-009)\n│   ├── AR-001/                         # CRD AgentRuntime type definition\n│   ├── AR-002/                         # CRD CodeInterpreter type definition\n│   ├── AR-003/                         # CRD shared types and constants\n│   ├── AR-004/ through AR-008/         # Various features\n│   └── AR-009/                         # Router HTTP reverse proxy core (IN PROGRESS)\n│       ├── proposal.md                 # Change proposal (template, mostly TODOs)\n│       ├── design.md                   # Design document (template, mostly TODOs)\n│       └── tasks.md                    # Task breakdown\n│\n├── session-routing/                    # Session routing design docs\n│   ├── design.md                       # Detailed router design (160 lines)\n│   └── spec.md                         # Session routing specification (115 lines)\n│\n├── session-store/                      # Session store design docs\n│   ├── design.md                       # Store interface (Redis/Valkey) design\n│   └── spec.md                         # Store specification\n│\n├── sandbox-orchestration/              # Sandbox orchestration design\n│   ├── design.md                       # Full design with go.mod deps reference\n│   └── spec.md                         # Orchestration specification\n│\n├── deployment/                         # Deployment design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   ├── spec.md\n│   └── client-go.md                    # Detailed client-go reference (256 lines)\n│\n├── ci-cd/                              # CI/CD design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── cli-toolkit/                        # CLI toolkit design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── code-execution/                     # Code execution design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── idle-cleanup/                       # Idle cleanup design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n├── integrations/                       # Integrations design\n│   └── design.md\n│\n├── python-sdk/                         # Python SDK design\n│   ├── design.md\n│   └── spec.md\n│\n└── testing/\n    └── agentcube_tdd_manifest.md       # TDD manifest with test requirements\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. Existing Router-Related Code in `pkg/router`\n\n**There is NO existing `pkg/router` directory or code.** The router module is planned but not yet implemented. However, there is extensive design documentation:\n\n- **`proposal.md`** (root): AR-009 proposal for \"Router HTTP Reverse Proxy Core\" -- outlines building a Go HTTP reverse proxy at `pkg/router` for routing to AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter instances.\n- **`delta-spec.md`** (root): Extremely detailed 821-line specification covering Config, Server, SessionManager, JWTManager, reverse proxy, concurrency middleware, health endpoints, CRD Informer integration, load balancing, backend health checks, and middleware.\n- **`session-routing/design.md`**: Detailed router design with exact struct definitions, route tables, JWT constants, reverse proxy behavior, and environment variables.\n- **`session-routing/spec.md`**: 115-line specification with Gherkin-style scenarios for session resolution, reverse proxy, JWT injection, error mapping, health endpoints, and concurrency limiting.\n- **`changes/AR-009/`**: Change request directory with template files (proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md) -- mostly TODO placeholders awaiting implementation.\n\nThe only router-related code reference is a constant in `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go`:\n```go\nIdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Design Document Patterns/Conventions\n\nThe project follows a consistent documentation structure:\n\n**Change Request (AR-XXX) Pattern:**\nEach change in `changes/AR-XXX/` contains:\n- `proposal.md` -- Change overview, scope, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria\n- `design.md` -- Technical implementation: architecture, data structures, API contracts, error handling, testing strategy, implementation steps\n- `tasks.md` -- Task breakdown\n- `delta-spec.md` (sometimes at root level) -- Detailed specification with Gherkin-style Given/When/Then scenarios\n\n**Domain Design Pattern:**\nEach domain folder (e.g., `session-routing/`, `session-store/`, `sandbox-orchestration/`) contains:\n- `design.md` -- Technical design with code snippets, struct definitions, behavior specifications\n- `spec.md` -- Requirements with Gherkin scenarios\n\n**Key Conventions:**\n- Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n- Gherkin scenarios: GIVEN/WHEN/THEN format\n- Go module path: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n- K8s API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n- Packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n\n---\n\n### 4. Key Dependencies and Frameworks\n\n**From `go.mod` (module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`, Go 1.25.0):**\n\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | v1.10.0 | HTTP web framework |\n| `github.com/google/uuid` | v1.6.0 | UUID generation |\n| `github.com/prometheus/client_golang` | v1.22.0 | Metrics/monitoring |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify` | v1.11.1 | Testing framework |\n| `k8s.io/api` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes API types |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes apimachinery |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes client library |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.22.2 | Controller-runtime framework |\n\n**Additional dependencies referenced in design docs (not yet in go.mod):**\n- `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` -- JWT RS256 signing\n- `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` -- Redis client\n- `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` -- Valkey client\n- `golang.org/x/net/http2` -- HTTP/2 support\n- `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` -- Agent sandbox CRDs\n\n**Code Generation Tools:**\n- `controller-gen` v0.17.2 -- DeepCopy + CRD YAML generation\n- `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 -- client-go code generation\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing HTTP Proxy / Reverse Proxy Implementations\n\n**There are NO existing reverse proxy implementations in the codebase.** The `pkg/router` package does not exist yet. However, the design is thoroughly specified:\n\n**Planned Reverse Proxy Architecture (from `session-routing/design.md` and `delta-spec.md`):**\n\n- **Core mechanism**: `net/http/httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy(targetURL)` with custom `http.Transport`\n- **Transport config**: `IdleConnTimeout: 0` (no idle connection recycling), `DisableCompression: false`\n- **Director function**: Sets `req.URL.Path`, clears `RawPath`, sets `req.Host`, adds forwarding headers (`X-Forwarded-Host`, `X-Forwarded-Proto`, `X-Forwarded-For`), optional JWT `Authorization` header\n- **ModifyResponse**: Sets `x-agentcube-session-id` response header\n- **Upstream URL resolution**: From `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` -- first matching path prefix, or first entry point; 404 if empty\n- **Error mapping**: `connection refused` -> 502, `timeout` -> 504, others -> 502\n- **Concurrency middleware**: Buffered channel semaphore, capacity `MaxConcurrentRequests` (default 1000), returns 429 when exhausted\n\n**Planned Route Table:**\n| Method | Path | Handler |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/health/live` | `handleHealthLive` |\n| GET | `/health/ready` | `handleHealthReady` |\n| GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n| GET/POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n\n**Planned Directory Structure (from `proposal.md`):**\n```\npkg/router/\n├── router.go          # Router interface and core implementation\n├── proxy.go           # ReverseProxy wrapper\n├── backend.go         # Backend management and health checks\n├── loadbalancer.go    # Load balancing strategies (Round-Robin, Least-Connections)\n├── middleware.go      # Middleware (logging, tracing, rate limiting)\n├── informer.go        # CRD Informer integration\n├── config.go          # Config struct\n├── server.go          # Server struct and constructor\n├── session_manager.go # SessionManager implementation\n├── jwt.go             # JWTManager and key management\n└── router_test.go     # Unit tests\n```\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Findings\n\n1. **`pkg/router` does not exist yet** -- it is the subject of AR-009, which is in the planning/specification phase with detailed design docs but no implementation code.\n\n2. **The project is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform** for AI agents, with CRDs (`AgentRuntime`, `CodeInterpreter`), a WorkloadManager controller, and a planned Router for session-aware HTTP proxying.\n\n3. **Design documentation is exceptionally thorough** -- the `delta-spec.md` alone is 821 lines with detailed Gherkin scenarios for every requirement.\n\n4. **The existing codebase** covers CRD type definitions (`pkg/apis`), WorkloadManager handlers and reconciler (`pkg/workloadmanager`), and generated client-go code.\n\n5. **The router will use** `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` (Go standard library) with Gin for routing, RS256 JWT for sandbox authentication, Redis/Valkey for session storage, and client-go Informers for dynamic service discovery.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28881dddcffeA8I1354cK4hdIt","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775826248224,"end":1775826382040}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775826382102,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d77802cdb001V64i5EOqgO8nGA","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d777de45c001uD4PMX2Jhkg3gy","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":19709,"input":19253,"output":216,"reasoning":240,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.006066684}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775826384197,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d77803542001wf4FSScTlQpVLE","messageID":"msg_d77802d2d001RjMbcTLsUTiF8B","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775826386406,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d77803980001Rg76O7TdE85boP","messageID":"msg_d77802d2d001RjMbcTLsUTiF8B","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5015bd47b1944f9ca8f4ca46","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 agentcube 项目新建 `pkg/router` 模块，实现基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心，作为系统的流量入口。该模块负责：(1) 通过 session ID 解析或创建 sandbox，(2) 将 HTTP 请求反向代理到 sandbox pod 的 entry point，(3) 为 sandbox 请求注入 RS256 JWT 签名，(4) 通过 client-go Informer 监听 CRD 变更实现动态服务发现，(5) 提供负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制中间件。本变更是对 AR-003（CRD 类型定义）、AR-005（Sandbox 创建）、AR-007（Reconciler）的下游消费方，同时解锁 AR-010+ 的高级流量治理能力。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: Config 结构体与 CLI 标志\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中定义 `Config` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n12: - `Port string` — 监听端口，默认 `\"8080\"`\n13: - `Debug bool` — 是否启用 Gin debug 模式，默认 `false`\n14: - `EnableTLS bool` — 是否启用 TLS，默认 `false`\n15: - `TLSCert string` — TLS 证书路径\n16: - `TLSKey string` — TLS 私钥路径\n17: - `MaxConcurrentRequests int` — 最大并发请求数，默认 `1000`（≤0 时 NewServer 内部设为 1000）\n18: \n19: `cmd/router/main.go` SHALL 解析以下 CLI 标志并构造 `Config`：\n20: \n21: | Flag | 类型 | 默认值 |\n22: |------|------|--------|\n23: | `-port` | string | `\"8080\"` |\n24: | `-debug` | bool | `false` |\n25: | `-enable-tls` | bool | `false` |\n26: | `-tls-cert` | string | `\"\"` |\n27: | `-tls-key` | string | `\"\"` |\n28: | `-max-concurrent-requests` | int | `1000` |\n29: \n30: #### Scenario: 默认配置\n31: \n32: - **GIVEN** 未传入任何 CLI 标志\n33: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n34: - **THEN** `Config.Port = \"8080\"`，`Config.Debug = false`，`Config.EnableTLS = false`，`Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 1000`\n35: \n36: #### Scenario: MaxConcurrentRequests 为 0 时 NewServer 设为 1000\n37: \n38: - **GIVEN** `Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 0`\n39: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n40: - **THEN** `config.MaxConcurrentRequests` 被设为 `1000`\n41: \n42: #### Scenario: 自定义配置覆盖默认值\n43: \n44: - **GIVEN** CLI 标志 `-port=9090 -debug -max-concurrent-requests=500`\n45: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n46: - **THEN** `Config.Port = \"9090\"`，`Config.Debug = true`，`Config.MaxConcurrentRequests = 500`\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ### Requirement: Server 结构体与构造函数\n51: \n52: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/server.go` 中定义 `Server` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n53: - `config *Config` — 配置\n54: - `engine *gin.Engine` — Gin 路由引擎\n55: - `httpServer *http.Server` — 标准库 HTTP 服务器\n56: - `sessionManager SessionManager` — 会话管理器接口\n57: - `storeClient store.Store` — Store 客户端\n58: - `httpTransport *http.Transport` — 共享 HTTP 传输层\n59: - `jwtManager *JWTManager` — JWT 管理器\n60: \n61: `httpTransport` SHALL 配置为：`IdleConnTimeout: 0`（不回收空闲连接），`DisableCompression: false`（启用压缩）。\n62: \n63: `NewServer(config *Config) (*Server, error)` SHALL：\n64: 1. 若 `config.MaxConcurrentRequests <= 0`，设为 `1000`\n65: 2. 构造 `httpTransport`\n66: 3. 初始化 Gin engine（`DebugMode` 若 `config.Debug`，否则 `ReleaseMode`）\n67: 4. 构造 `JWTManager` 并调用 `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret`，失败则返回错误（in-cluster 跳过路径除外）\n68: 5. 构造 `SessionManager`（读取 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 环境变量）\n69: 6. 构造 `store.Store` 实例\n70: 7. 注册路由\n71: 8. 构造 `httpServer`\n72: \n73: #### Scenario: Debug 模式设置\n74: \n75: - **GIVEN** `config.Debug = true`\n76: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n77: - **THEN** `gin.SetMode(gin.DebugMode)`\n78: \n79: #### Scenario: Release 模式设置\n80: \n81: - **GIVEN** `config.Debug = false`\n82: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n83: - **THEN** `gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)`\n84: \n85: #### Scenario: JWT 密钥初始化失败导致 Server 创建失败\n86: \n87: - **GIVEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret` 返回非 nil 错误且非 in-cluster skip 路径\n88: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 被调用\n89: - **THEN** 返回错误，Server 不为 nil 的条件不满足\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 未设置导致 Server 创建失败\n92: \n93: - **GIVEN** 环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置\n94: - **WHEN** `NewServer(config)` 构造 SessionManager\n95: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n96: \n97: ---\n98: \n99: ### Requirement: SessionManager 接口\n100: \n101: The system SHALL 定义 `SessionManager` 接口：\n102: \n103: ```go\n104: type SessionManager interface {\n105:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n106: }\n107: ```\n108: \n109: #### Scenario: 接口方法签名\n110: \n111: - **GIVEN** `SessionManager` 接口定义\n112: - **WHEN** 编译 `pkg/router`\n113: - **THEN** 接口包含 `GetSandboxBySession` 方法，签名如上\n114: \n115: ---\n116: \n117: ### Requirement: Session Manager 实现\n118: \n119: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中实现 `SessionManager` 接口：\n120: \n121: `manager` 结构体包含：\n122: - `storeClient store.Store`\n123: - `workloadMgrAddr string`\n124: - `httpClient *http.Client`\n125: \n126: `NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)` SHALL：\n127: 1. 读取环境变量 `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`，为空则返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n128: 2. 构造 `http.Client`：`Timeout: 2 * time.Minute`\n129: 3. 构造 `http.Transport`：`MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`，`DisableCompression: false`\n130: 4. 调用 `http2.ConfigureTransports` 配置 `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`，`PingTimeout: 15s`\n131: \n132: `GetSandboxBySession` SHALL：\n133: 1. 若 `sessionID` 非空，调用 `storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` 获取 `SandboxInfo`\n134: 2. 若 Store 返回 `ErrNotFound`，返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)`\n135: 3. 若 `sessionID` 为空，POST 到 WorkloadManager 创建 sandbox\n136: 4. 创建请求的 URL：`AgentRuntime` → `{addr}/v1/agent-runtime`，`CodeInterpreter` → `{addr}/v1/code-interpreter`\n137: 5. 请求体：JSON `{\"kind\":\"<kind>\",\"name\":\"<name>\",\"namespace\":\"<namespace>\"}`\n138: 6. 若 `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且可读，附加 `Authorization: Bearer <trimmed contents>`\n139: 7. 响应 200 时解析 `CreateSandboxResponse`，构建 `SandboxInfo`\n140: 8. 响应非 200 时返回 `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind)`\n141: 9. 若响应体 `sessionId` 为空，返回内部错误\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: 缺失 WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL 导致构造失败\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置\n146: - **WHEN** `NewSessionManager(storeClient)` 被调用\n147: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL environment variable is not set\"`\n148: \n149: #### Scenario: 已知 sessionID 从 Store 获取 SandboxInfo\n150: \n151: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n152: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-001\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n153: - **THEN** 返回对应的 `*types.SandboxInfo`\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: 未知 sessionID 返回 SessionNotFoundError\n156: \n157: - **GIVEN** Store 中不存在 `sess-unknown` 条目\n158: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-unknown\", ...)` 被调用\n159: - **THEN** 返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(\"sess-unknown\")`\n160: \n161: #### Scenario: 空 sessionID 触发 WorkloadManager 创建\n162: \n163: - **GIVEN** `sessionID` 为空字符串，`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 已设置\n164: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n165: - **THEN** POST JSON `{\"kind\":\"AgentRuntime\",\"name\":\"my-runtime\",\"namespace\":\"default\"}` 到 `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`\n166: \n167: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager 非 200 返回模板未找到错误\n168: \n169: - **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 HTTP 404\n170: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被处理\n171: - **THEN** 返回 `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(\"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")`\n172: \n173: #### Scenario: 创建响应 sessionId 为空返回内部错误\n174: \n175: - **GIVEN** WorkloadManager 返回 HTTP 200，但响应体 `sessionId` 字段为空\n176: - **WHEN** 响应被解析\n177: - **THEN** 返回内部错误\n178: \n179: #### Scenario: In-cluster token 附加到创建请求\n180: \n181: - **GIVEN** `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 存在且包含 `\"token-abc123\"`\n182: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被发送\n183: - **THEN** 请求携带 `Authorization: Bearer token-abc123`\n184: \n185: #### Scenario: Service account token 文件不存在时不附加 Auth header\n186: \n187: - **GIVEN** `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` 不存在\n188: - **WHEN** 空 sessionID 的创建请求被发送\n189: - **THEN** 请求不携带 `Authorization` header，不 panic\n190: \n191: ---\n192: \n193: ### Requirement: JWTManager 与密钥管理\n194: \n195: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/jwt.go` 中定义 `JWTManager`：\n196: \n197: **常量：**\n198: \n199: | 名称 | 值 |\n200: |------|-----|\n201: | `rsaKeySize` | `2048` |\n202: | `jwtExpiration` | `5 * time.Minute` |\n203: | `IdentitySecretName` | `\"picod-router-identity\"` |\n204: | `PrivateKeyDataKey` | `\"private.pem\"` |\n205: | `PublicKeyDataKey` | `\"public.pem\"` |\n206: \n207: **变量：**\n208: - `IdentityNamespace` — 初始值 `\"default\"`，`init()` 中若 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` 环境变量存在则覆盖\n209: \n210: ```go\n211: type JWTManager struct {\n212:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n213:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n214:     clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n215: }\n216: ```\n217: \n218: `NewJWTManager()` SHALL 生成 RSA 2048-bit 密钥对（`rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)`）。\n219: \n220: `GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error)` SHALL：\n221: 1. 设置基础 claims：`exp` = now + jwtExpiration（Unix 时间戳），`iat` = now（Unix 时间戳），`iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"`\n222: 2. 合并自定义 claims\n223: 3. 使用 `jwt.SigningMethodRS256` 签名，返回 JWT 字符串\n224: \n225: `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx) error` SHALL：\n226: 1. 若 `clientset == nil`，尝试 `rest.InClusterConfig()`；失败则 log warning 并返回 nil（ephemeral keys 路径）\n227: 2. 构造 Secret：`IdentitySecretName`，namespace 为 `IdentityNamespace`，type `Opaque`，labels `app=agentcube` + `component=router`，data 包含 `private.pem`（PKCS1 PEM）和 `public.pem`（PKIX PEM）\n228: 3. 尝试 Create；若 `AlreadyExists`，Get Secret 并调用 `loadPrivateKeyPEM` 加载私钥\n229: \n230: #### Scenario: 新集群中创建 JWT Secret\n231: \n232: - **GIVEN** in-cluster config 成功，Secret `picod-router-identity` 不存在\n233: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n234: - **THEN** 创建 opaque Secret，包含 `private.pem` 和 `public.pem`\n235: \n236: #### Scenario: 已存在 Secret 时加载私钥\n237: \n238: - **GIVEN** Secret `picod-router-identity` 已存在\n239: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n240: - **THEN** 不创建新 Secret，从 Secret 中加载 `private.pem` 到 `privateKey`\n241: \n242: #### Scenario: 非 in-cluster 环境使用 ephemeral keys\n243: \n244: - **GIVEN** `clientset == nil` 且 `rest.InClusterConfig()` 失败\n245: - **WHEN** `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)` 被调用\n246: - **THEN** 发出 warning 日志，返回 nil，使用内存中的 ephemeral 密钥对\n247: \n248: #### Scenario: JWT token 包含标准 claims\n249: \n250: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已初始化\n251: - **WHEN** `GenerateToken(map[string]interface{}{\"session_id\": \"sess-001\"})` 被调用\n252: - **THEN** 返回的 JWT 包含 `exp`（5 分钟后）、`iat`（当前时间）、`iss`（`\"agentcube-router\"`）和 `session_id`（`\"sess-001\"`）\n253: \n254: #### Scenario: JWT 使用 RS256 算法签名\n255: \n256: - **GIVEN** `JWTManager` 已初始化\n257: - **WHEN** `GenerateToken(...)` 被调用\n258: - **THEN** JWT header 中 `alg` 为 `\"RS256\"`\n259: \n260: #### Scenario: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 覆盖默认 namespace\n261: \n262: - **GIVEN** 环境变量 `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE = \"agentcube-prod\"`\n263: - **WHEN** 包初始化完成\n264: - **THEN** `IdentityNamespace = \"agentcube-prod\"`\n265: \n266: ---\n267: \n268: ### Requirement: 反向代理到 Sandbox\n269: \n270: The system SHALL 使用 `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy(targetURL)` 构建反向代理，`proxy.Transport = s.httpTransport`。\n271: \n272: Upstream URL 确定逻辑：\n273: 1. 从 `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 中查找第一个 `path` 前缀匹配 invocation path 的 entry point\n274: 2. 若无匹配，使用第一个 entry point\n275: 3. 若 `EntryPoints` 为空，返回 404 JSON `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n276: \n277: URL 构建：若 `protocol` 已设置且 `endpoint` 不含 scheme，则在 `endpoint` 前拼接 `protocol`（小写）+ `\"://\"`。\n278: \n279: Director SHALL：\n280: 1. 设置 `req.URL.Path` 为规范化后的路径（Gin path param 若无前导 `/` 则添加）\n281: 2. 清除 `req.URL.RawPath`\n282: 3. 设置 `req.Host = targetURL.Host`\n283: 4. 设置转发 headers（见 Requirement: Forwarding headers）\n284: 5. 若 JWT 非空，设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n285: \n286: ModifyResponse SHALL 设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID。\n287: \n288: #### Scenario: EntryPoints 为空返回 404\n289: \n290: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 为空切片\n291: - **WHEN** 反向代理处理请求\n292: - **THEN** 响应 404，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n293: \n294: #### Scenario: 匹配 path 前缀选择 entry point\n295: \n296: - **GIVEN** `EntryPoints` 包含两个 entry：`{path: \"/api\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8080\"}` 和 `{path: \"/ws\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8081\"}`\n297: - **AND** invocation path 为 `/api/users`\n298: - **WHEN** upstream 被确定\n299: - **THEN** 选择第一个 entry point（`/api` 匹配）\n300: \n301: #### Scenario: 无匹配时使用第一个 entry point\n302: \n303: - **GIVEN** `EntryPoints` 包含 `{path: \"/api\", endpoint: \"sandbox:8080\"}`\n304: - **AND** invocation path 为 `/other/path`\n305: - **WHEN** upstream 被确定\n306: - **THEN** 使用第一个 entry point\n307: \n308: #### Scenario: Endpoint 不含 scheme 时拼接 protocol\n309: \n310: - **GIVEN** entry point `protocol = \"http\"`，`endpoint = \"sandbox:8080\"`\n311: - **WHEN** upstream URL 被构建\n312: - **THEN** 目标 URL 为 `http://sandbox:8080`\n313: \n314: #### Scenario: Path 无前导斜杠时自动添加\n315: \n316: - **GIVEN** Gin path param `*path` 值为 `\"users/123\"`（无前导 `/`）\n317: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n318: - **THEN** `req.URL.Path` 被设为 `\"/users/123\"`\n319: \n320: #### Scenario: ModifyResponse 设置 session ID header\n321: \n322: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `\"sess-001\"`\n323: - **WHEN** 代理响应返回\n324: - **THEN** 响应 header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-001`\n325: \n326: ---\n327: \n328: ### Requirement: JWT 注入\n329: \n330: For sandbox kinds `Sandbox` 和 `SandboxClaim`，the system SHALL 在代理前生成 JWT 并设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 到代理请求。\n331: \n332: #### Scenario: JWT 签名失败返回 500\n333: \n334: - **GIVEN** JWT 生成返回错误\n335: - **WHEN** 转发请求\n336: - **THEN** 响应 500，body 为 JSON 包含 `\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"` 和 `\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"`\n337: \n338: #### Scenario: 非 Sandbox/SandboxClaim kind 不注入 JWT\n339: \n340: - **GIVEN** sandbox kind 为 `PicoD`\n341: - **WHEN** 代理请求被构建\n342: - **THEN** 不设置 `Authorization` header\n343: \n344: ---\n345: \n346: ### Requirement: Forwarding headers 与响应 header\n347: \n348: The system SHALL 在 Director 中设置以下转发 headers：\n349: - `X-Forwarded-Host`：来自原始请求的 `Host`\n350: - `X-Forwarded-Proto`：TLS 存在时为 `\"https\"`，否则 `\"http\"`\n351: - `X-Forwarded-For`：将客户端 IP 追加到已有值（逗号分隔）\n352: \n353: The system SHALL 在 ModifyResponse 中设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID。\n354: \n355: #### Scenario: X-Forwarded-For 追加客户端 IP\n356: \n357: - **GIVEN** 原始请求已有 `X-Forwarded-For: 1.2.3.4`\n358: - **AND** 客户端 IP 为 `5.6.7.8`\n359: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n360: - **THEN** `X-Forwarded-For` 被设为 `\"1.2.3.4, 5.6.7.8\"`\n361: \n362: #### Scenario: X-Forwarded-Proto 为 http\n363: \n364: - **GIVEN** 请求未使用 TLS\n365: - **WHEN** Director 运行\n366: - **THEN** `X-Forwarded-Proto` 被设为 `\"http\"`\n367: \n368: ---\n369: \n370: ### Requirement: 代理错误映射\n371: \n372: The system SHALL 在 `ErrorHandler` 中映射代理错误：\n373: - 错误信息包含 `\"connection refused\"` → 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n374: - 错误信息包含 `\"timeout\"` → 504 `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}`\n375: - 其他错误 → 502 `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n376: \n377: #### Scenario: 下游连接被拒绝\n378: \n379: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息包含 `\"connection refused\"`\n380: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n381: - **THEN** 响应 502，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n382: \n383: #### Scenario: 下游超时\n384: \n385: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息包含 `\"timeout\"`\n386: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n387: - **THEN** 响应 504，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}`\n388: \n389: #### Scenario: 其他代理错误\n390: \n391: - **GIVEN** 反向代理错误信息为 `\"dial tcp: lookup sandbox: no such host\"`\n392: - **WHEN** `ErrorHandler` 运行\n393: - **THEN** 响应 502，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}`\n394: \n395: ---\n396: \n397: ### Requirement: Last-activity 更新\n398: \n399: The system SHALL 在成功解析 sandbox 后调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, time.Now())`，并在 `forwardToSandbox` 返回后再次调用（每次成功 invoke 路径调用两次）。失败 SHALL 仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程。\n400: \n401: #### Scenario: Store 更新失败不阻断代理\n402: \n403: - **GIVEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 返回错误\n404: - **WHEN** sandbox 解析成功\n405: - **THEN** 代理仍然执行，错误仅被记录为 warning\n406: \n407: #### Scenario: 成功路径调用两次 UpdateSessionLastActivity\n408: \n409: - **GIVEN** sandbox 解析成功且代理转发成功\n410: - **WHEN** invoke handler 完成\n411: - **THEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 被调用两次（解析后和转发后）\n412: \n413: ---\n414: \n415: ### Requirement: Health 端点\n416: \n417: The system SHALL 注册以下 health 端点：\n418: \n419: | Method | Path | Handler | 响应 |\n420: |--------|------|---------|------|\n421: | GET | `/health/live` | `handleHealthLive` | 200 `{\"status\":\"alive\"}` |\n422: | GET | `/health/ready` | `handleHealthReady` | 见下 |\n423: \n424: `handleHealthReady` SHALL：\n425: - 若 `sessionManager` 非 nil，返回 200 `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`\n426: - 若 `sessionManager` 为 nil，返回 503 `{\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}`\n427: \n428: Health 端点 SHALL 不经过任何中间件（无 logger、recovery、concurrency limit）。\n429: \n430: #### Scenario: Liveness 始终返回 200\n431: \n432: - **GIVEN** Server 已启动\n433: - **WHEN** `GET /health/live` 被请求\n434: - **THEN** 响应 200，body 为 JSON `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`\n435: \n436: #### Scenario: Readiness 依赖 sessionManager\n437: \n438: - **GIVEN** `sessionManager` 为 nil\n439: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` 被请求\n440: - **THEN** 响应 503，body 包含 `\"error\":\"session manager not available\"`\n441: \n442: #### Scenario: Readiness 返回 200 当 sessionManager 可用\n443: \n444: - **GIVEN** `sessionManager` 非 nil\n445: - **WHEN** `GET /health/ready` 被请求\n446: - **THEN** 响应 200，body 为 JSON `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`\n447: \n448: ---\n449: \n450: ### Requirement: 并发限制中间件\n451: \n452: The system SHALL 实现基于 buffered channel 的信号量中间件 `concurrencyLimitMiddleware`，容量为 `config.MaxConcurrentRequests`。\n453: \n454: 中间件行为：\n455: 1. 尝试向 channel 发送（非阻塞 `select` + `default`）\n456: 2. 若发送成功，执行 `c.Next()`，完成后从 channel 接收释放槽位\n457: 3. 若发送失败（无可用槽位），响应 429 JSON `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}` 并 `c.Abort()`\n458: \n459: 该中间件 SHALL 仅应用于 `/v1` 路由组，不应用于 health 端点。\n460: \n461: #### Scenario: 并发槽位可用时请求通过\n462: \n463: - **GIVEN** 当前并发数 < `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n464: - **WHEN** 请求到达 `/v1/...` 路由\n465: - **THEN** 请求被正常处理\n466: \n467: #### Scenario: 并发槽位耗尽时返回 429\n468: \n469: - **GIVEN** 当前并发数 = `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n470: - **WHEN** 新请求到达 `/v1/...` 路由\n471: - **THEN** 响应 429，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}`\n472: \n473: #### Scenario: 请求完成后释放槽位\n474: \n475: - **GIVEN** 一个请求占用了并发槽位\n476: - **WHEN** 请求处理完成\n477: - **THEN** 槽位被释放，可被后续请求使用\n478: \n479: #### Scenario: Health 端点不受并发限制\n480: \n481: - **GIVEN** 并发槽位已耗尽\n482: - **WHEN** `GET /health/live` 被请求\n483: - **THEN** 请求正常处理，返回 200\n484: \n485: ---\n486: \n487: ### Requirement: 调用路由注册\n488: \n489: The system SHALL 注册以下路由到 Gin engine：\n490: \n491: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n492: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n493: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n494: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n495: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n496: | POST | 同上 | 同上 | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n497: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n498: | POST | 同上 | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n499: \n500: `/v1` 路由组 SHALL 使用 `gin.Logger()`、`gin.Recovery()` 和 `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` 中间件。\n501: \n502: `handleAgentInvoke` SHALL 以 `types.AgentRuntimeKind` 作为 kind 参数调用 session lookup。\n503: `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` SHALL 以 `types.CodeInterpreterKind` 作为 kind 参数调用 session lookup。\n504: \n505: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 调用使用正确的 kind\n506: \n507: - **GIVEN** 请求 `GET /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/api/users`\n508: - **WHEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 运行\n509: - **THEN** kind 参数为 `types.AgentRuntimeKind`\n510: \n511: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 调用使用正确的 kind\n512: \n513: - **GIVEN** 请求 `POST /v1/namespaces/default/code-interpreters/my-ci/invocations/execute`\n514: - **WHEN** `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` 运行\n515: - **THEN** kind 参数为 `types.CodeInterpreterKind`\n516: \n517: #### Scenario: GET 和 POST 均支持\n518: \n519: - **GIVEN** 路由已注册\n520: - **WHEN** `GET /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/` 被请求\n521: - **THEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 被调用\n522: - **WHEN** `POST /v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/my-runtime/invocations/` 被请求\n523: - **THEN** `handleAgentInvoke` 被调用\n524: \n525: ---\n526: \n527: ### Requirement: HTTP 服务器行为\n528: \n529: The system SHALL 配置 `http.Server`：\n530: - `ReadTimeout: 30 * time.Second`\n531: - `IdleTimeout: 90 * time.Second`\n532: - 使用 `h2c` 和 `http2.Server` 支持 HTTP/2 明文升级\n533: \n534: `Start()` 方法 SHALL：\n535: 1. 若 `config.EnableTLS = true` 且 `TLSCert` 或 `TLSKey` 为空，返回错误 `\"TLS cert and key must both be provided\"`\n536: 2. 若 TLS 启用，调用 `httpServer.ListenAndServeTLS(config.TLSCert, config.TLSKey)`\n537: 3. 否则调用支持 h2c 的启动方式\n538: \n539: `Stop(ctx)` 方法 SHALL：\n540: 1. 在 context 取消时调用 `httpServer.Shutdown(ctx)`\n541: 2. Shutdown 超时 10 秒\n542: \n543: #### Scenario: TLS 配置不完整返回错误\n544: \n545: - **GIVEN** `config.EnableTLS = true` 且 `config.TLSCert = \"\"`\n546: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n547: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"TLS cert and key must both be provided\"`\n548: \n549: #### Scenario: 正常启动无 TLS\n550: \n551: - **GIVEN** `config.EnableTLS = false`\n552: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n553: - **THEN** 服务器在 `config.Port` 上监听，支持 h2c\n554: \n555: #### Scenario: 优雅关闭在 10 秒内完成\n556: \n557: - **GIVEN** 服务器正在运行，有活跃连接\n558: - **WHEN** context 被取消\n559: - **THEN** `httpServer.Shutdown` 在 10 秒超时内完成\n560: \n561: ---\n562: \n563: ### Requirement: CRD Informer 集成\n564: \n565: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/informer.go` 中使用 `client-go` 的 Informer 机制监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 变更：\n566: \n567: 1. 使用 `SharedInformerFactory`（`informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(clientset, 30*time.Second)`）\n568: 2. 获取 `agentRuntimeInformer = factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()`\n569: 3. 获取 `codeInterpreterInformer = factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters()`\n570: 4. 注册事件处理器：\n571: \n572: ```go\n573: agentRuntimeInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n574:     AddFunc:    onAgentRuntimeAdded,\n575:     UpdateFunc: onAgentRuntimeUpdated,\n576:     DeleteFunc: onAgentRuntimeDeleted,\n577: })\n578: ```\n579: \n580: 5. 使用 `Lister` 接口进行本地缓存查询，减少 API Server 压力\n581: 6. Informer 启动后调用 `factory.Start(stopCh)` 和 `factory.WaitForCacheSync(stopCh)`\n582: \n583: 事件处理器 SHALL 更新内部路由表（`AddRoute`/`RemoveRoute`）。\n584: \n585: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 AgentRuntime 新增\n586: \n587: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n588: - **WHEN** 新的 AgentRuntime CR 被创建\n589: - **THEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被调用，路由表被更新\n590: \n591: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 CodeInterpreter 更新\n592: \n593: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n594: - **WHEN** CodeInterpreter CR 被更新\n595: - **THEN** `onCodeInterpreterUpdated` 被调用，路由表被更新\n596: \n597: #### Scenario: Informer 监听 CR 删除\n598: \n599: - **GIVEN** Informer 已启动并同步\n600: - **WHEN** AgentRuntime CR 被删除\n601: - **THEN** `onAgentRuntimeDeleted` 被调用，对应路由从路由表移除\n602: \n603: #### Scenario: Lister 查询不经过 API Server\n604: \n605: - **GIVEN** Informer 缓存已同步\n606: - **WHEN** 通过 Lister 查询 AgentRuntime 列表\n607: - **THEN** 请求命中本地缓存，不产生 K8s API 调用\n608: \n609: ---\n610: \n611: ### Requirement: 路由管理（AddRoute/RemoveRoute）\n612: \n613: The system SHALL 实现 `Router` 接口：\n614: \n615: ```go\n616: type Router interface {\n617:     AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n618:     RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n619:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n620: }\n621: \n622: type Backend struct {\n623:     URL      *url.URL\n624:     Weight   int\n625:     Healthy  bool\n626: }\n627: ```\n628: \n629: `AddRoute` SHALL：\n630: 1. 验证 `pattern` 非空\n631: 2. 若 pattern 已存在，返回错误（或更新，见 tradeoff）\n632: 3. 将 pattern → Backend 映射存入路由表\n633: 4. 线程安全（使用 `sync.RWMutex` 保护）\n634: \n635: `RemoveRoute` SHALL：\n636: 1. 从路由表中移除 pattern\n637: 2. 若 pattern 不存在，返回 nil（幂等）\n638: 3. 线程安全\n639: \n640: `ServeHTTP` SHALL：\n641: 1. 根据请求路径匹配路由\n642: 2. 选择健康的 backend（负载均衡策略）\n643: 3. 若无匹配路由，返回 404\n644: 4. 代理请求到选中的 backend\n645: \n646: #### Scenario: 添加新路由\n647: \n648: - **GIVEN** 路由表为空\n649: - **WHEN** `AddRoute(\"/api/v1\", Backend{URL: &url.URL{Host: \"backend:8080\"}})` 被调用\n650: - **THEN** 路由表中存在该映射\n651: \n652: #### Scenario: 重复添加同一路由返回错误\n653: \n654: - **GIVEN** 路由表中已存在 pattern `\"/api/v1\"`\n655: - **WHEN** `AddRoute(\"/api/v1\", ...)` 再次被调用\n656: - **THEN** 返回错误\n657: \n658: #### Scenario: 移除不存在的路由幂等返回 nil\n659: \n660: - **GIVEN** 路由表中不存在 pattern `\"/api/v2\"`\n661: - **WHEN** `RemoveRoute(\"/api/v2\")` 被调用\n662: - **THEN** 返回 nil，无错误\n663: \n664: #### Scenario: 并发添加删路由不产生 data race\n665: \n666: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 同时调用 `AddRoute` 和 `RemoveRoute`\n667: - **WHEN** 操作执行\n668: - **THEN** 无 data race，路由表状态一致\n669: \n670: #### Scenario: 无匹配路由返回 404\n671: \n672: - **GIVEN** 请求路径 `/unknown/path`\n673: - **AND** 路由表中无匹配项\n674: - **WHEN** `ServeHTTP` 被调用\n675: - **THEN** 响应 404\n676: \n677: ---\n678: \n679: ### Requirement: 负载均衡策略\n680: \n681: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/loadbalancer.go` 中实现以下负载均衡策略：\n682: \n683: **Round-Robin：**\n684: - 按顺序循环选择 backend\n685: - 跳过不健康的 backend\n686: - 线程安全的计数器\n687: \n688: **Least-Connections：**\n689: - 选择当前活跃连接数最少的健康 backend\n690: - 使用原子计数器跟踪连接数\n691: \n692: 策略选择 SHALL 可通过配置指定，默认 Round-Robin。\n693: \n694: #### Scenario: Round-Robin 循环选择\n695: \n696: - **GIVEN** 三个健康 backend：A、B、C\n697: - **WHEN** 连续三次选择\n698: - **THEN** 依次选择 A、B、C\n699: \n700: #### Scenario: Round-Robin 跳过不健康 backend\n701: \n702: - **GIVEN** 三个 backend：A（健康）、B（不健康）、C（健康）\n703: - **WHEN** Round-Robin 选择\n704: - **THEN** 只选择 A 和 C，跳过 B\n705: \n706: #### Scenario: 所有 backend 不健康\n707: \n708: - **GIVEN** 所有 backend 的 `Healthy = false`\n709: - **WHEN** 负载均衡选择 backend\n710: - **THEN** 返回错误 `\"no healthy backend available\"`\n711: \n712: #### Scenario: Least-Connections 选择连接数最少的\n713: \n714: - **GIVEN** Backend A 有 5 个活跃连接，Backend B 有 2 个\n715: - **WHEN** Least-Connections 策略选择\n716: - **THEN** 选择 Backend B\n717: \n718: ---\n719: \n720: ### Requirement: Backend 健康检查\n721: \n722: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/backend.go` 中实现 backend 健康检查：\n723: \n724: 1. 定期对每个 backend 的 `URL` 发送 HTTP GET 请求（默认 `/health` 路径，30 秒间隔）\n725: 2. 响应 2xx 标记为 `Healthy = true`\n726: 3. 响应非 2xx 或超时标记为 `Healthy = false`\n727: 4. 连续失败 N 次（默认 3 次）后才标记为不健康（避免抖动）\n728: 5. 连续成功 M 次（默认 2 次）后才标记为健康（避免抖动）\n729: \n730: #### Scenario: 健康检查成功标记为健康\n731: \n732: - **GIVEN** backend 连续 2 次健康检查返回 200\n733: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n734: - **THEN** `Healthy = true`\n735: \n736: #### Scenario: 健康检查连续失败标记为不健康\n737: \n738: - **GIVEN** backend 连续 3 次健康检查返回 500\n739: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n740: - **THEN** `Healthy = false`\n741: \n742: #### Scenario: 单次失败不立即标记为不健康\n743: \n744: - **GIVEN** backend 之前健康，本次健康检查返回 500\n745: - **AND** 连续失败次数为 1（阈值 3）\n746: - **WHEN** 健康状态被评估\n747: - **THEN** `Healthy` 保持 `true`\n748: \n749: ---\n750: \n751: ### Requirement: 中间件（日志、追踪、限流）\n752: \n753: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/middleware.go` 中实现以下中间件：\n754: \n755: **请求日志中间件：**\n756: - 记录请求方法、路径、响应状态码、耗时\n757: - 使用结构化日志（`slog`）\n758: \n759: **Trace ID 注入中间件：**\n760: - 生成唯一 Trace ID（UUID v4）\n761: - 设置请求 header `X-Trace-Id`\n762: - 设置响应 header `X-Trace-Id`\n763: \n764: **基础限流中间件（可选）：**\n765: - 基于令牌桶算法\n766: - 默认速率：100 req/s，桶容量 200\n767: - 超限返回 429\n768: \n769: #### Scenario: Trace ID 注入请求和响应\n770: \n771: - **GIVEN** 请求到达\n772: - **WHEN** Trace ID 中间件运行\n773: - **THEN** 请求 header 包含 `X-Trace-Id: <uuid>`\n774: - **AND** 响应 header 包含 `X-Trace-Id: <uuid>`（相同值）\n775: \n776: #### Scenario: 请求日志包含方法和耗时\n777: \n778: - **GIVEN** 请求 `GET /v1/...` 耗时 150ms\n779: - **WHEN** 请求完成\n780: - **THEN** 日志包含 `method=GET`，`path=/v1/...`，`status=200`，`duration_ms=150`\n781: \n782: ---\n783: \n784: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n785: \n786: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n787: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n788: 2. `go build ./cmd/router/...` 编译通过\n789: 3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n790: 4. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n791: 5. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（使用 `slog` 或 `klog`）\n792: \n793: #### Scenario: pkg/router 编译通过\n794: \n795: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n796: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n797: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n798: \n799: #### Scenario: cmd/router 编译通过\n800: \n801: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n802: - **WHEN** `go build ./cmd/router/...` 执行\n803: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n804: \n805: #### Scenario: 所有单元测试通过\n806: \n807: - **GIVEN** 测试用例已编写\n808: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 执行\n809: - **THEN** 所有测试通过\n810: \n811: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n812: \n813: - **GIVEN** 并发场景测试已覆盖（路由表、负载均衡、健康检查）\n814: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n815: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n816: \n817: #### Scenario: 无 log.Printf 残留\n818: \n819: - **GIVEN** 所有日志已使用 `slog` 或 `klog`\n820: - **WHEN** `grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/` 执行\n821: - **THEN** 无匹配结果\n\n(End of file - total 821 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 agentcube 项目新建 `pkg/router` 模块，实现基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心，作为系统的流量入口。该模块负责：(1) 通过 session ID 解析或创建 sandbox，(2) 将 HTTP 请求反向代理到 sandbox pod 的 entry point，(3) 为 sandbox 请求注入 RS256 JWT 签名，(4) 通过 client-go Informer 监听 CRD 变更实现动态服务发现，(5) 提供负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制中间件。本变更是对 AR-003（CRD 类型定义）、AR-005（Sandbox 创建）、AR-007（Reconciler）的下游消费方，同时解锁 AR-010+ 的高级流量治理能力。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: Config 结构体与 CLI 标志\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中定义 `Config` 结构体，包含以下字段：\n- `Port string` — 监听端口，默认 `\"8080\"`\n- `Debug bool` — 是否启用 Gin debug 模式，默认 `false`\n- `EnableTLS bool` — 是否启用 TLS，默认 `false`\n- `TLSCert string` — TLS 证书路径\n- `TLSKey string` — TLS 私钥路径\n- `MaxConcurrentRequests int` — 最大并发请求数，默认 `1000`（≤0 时 NewServer 内部设为 1000）\n\n`cmd/router/main.go` SHALL 解析以下 CLI 标志并构造 `Config`：\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775826386396,"end":1775826386403}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775826387493,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d77803e9f001XvPWSIJxEMMnGK","messageID":"msg_d77802d2d001RjMbcTLsUTiF8B","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c1edd982d7524ba29d4812d8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Session Routing — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - Same repository: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see sandbox-orchestration design for `go.mod` and versions).\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router`\n8: \n9: ### Config\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: const LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n13: \n14: type Config struct {\n15:     Port                  string\n16:     Debug                 bool\n17:     EnableTLS             bool\n18:     TLSCert               string\n19:     TLSKey                string\n20:     MaxConcurrentRequests int  // 0 = unlimited at flag level; NewServer coerces to 1000\n21: }\n22: ```\n23: \n24: ### CLI flags (`cmd/router/main.go`)\n25: \n26: | Flag | Default |\n27: |------|---------|\n28: | `-port` | `8080` |\n29: | `-enable-tls` | `false` |\n30: | `-tls-cert` | `\"\"` |\n31: | `-tls-key` | `\"\"` |\n32: | `-debug` | `false` |\n33: | `-max-concurrent-requests` | `1000` (0 means unlimited per flag help; `NewServer` still sets default 1000 when `<= 0`) |\n34: \n35: ### Server struct\n36: \n37: ```go\n38: type Server struct {\n39:     config         *Config\n40:     engine         *gin.Engine\n41:     httpServer     *http.Server\n42:     sessionManager SessionManager\n43:     storeClient    store.Store\n44:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n45:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n46: }\n47: ```\n48: \n49: - `httpTransport`: `IdleConnTimeout: 0`, `DisableCompression: false`.\n50: - Store: `store.Storage()` for both session manager and `storeClient`.\n51: - Gin mode: `DebugMode` if `config.Debug`, else `ReleaseMode`.\n52: \n53: ### Route table\n54: \n55: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n56: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n57: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n58: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n59: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n60: | POST | same | same | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n61: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | same | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n62: | POST | same | same | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n63: \n64: ### SessionManager interface\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: type SessionManager interface {\n68:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n69: }\n70: ```\n71: \n72: ### manager implementation (`session_manager.go`)\n73: \n74: ```go\n75: type manager struct {\n76:     storeClient     store.Store\n77:     workloadMgrAddr string\n78:     httpClient      *http.Client\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: - `NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)` reads `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` (required).\n83: - HTTP client: `Timeout: 2 * time.Minute`; transport `MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`, `DisableCompression: false`; `http2.ConfigureTransports` with `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`, `PingTimeout: 15s`.\n84: - Endpoints: `AgentRuntime` → `{WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL}/v1/agent-runtime`; `CodeInterpreter` → `.../v1/code-interpreter`.\n85: - Request: `Content-Type: application/json`; optional `Authorization: Bearer` from `loadWorkloadManagerAuthToken()` reading `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` (trimmed); missing file → no header (warning if non-NotExist error).\n86: \n87: ### JWT (`jwt.go`)\n88: \n89: **Constants (unexported unless noted):**\n90: \n91: | Name | Value |\n92: |------|--------|\n93: | `rsaKeySize` | `2048` |\n94: | `jwtExpiration` | `5 * time.Minute` |\n95: | `IdentitySecretName` | `\"picod-router-identity\"` |\n96: | `PrivateKeyDataKey` | `\"private.pem\"` |\n97: | `PublicKeyDataKey` | `\"public.pem\"` |\n98: \n99: ```go\n100: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\" // init: AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE if set\n101: ```\n102: \n103: **JWTManager:**\n104: \n105: ```go\n106: type JWTManager struct {\n107:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n108:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n109:     clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n110: }\n111: ```\n112: \n113: - `NewJWTManager()`: `rsa.GenerateKey(rand.Reader, rsaKeySize)`.\n114: - `GenerateToken(claims map[string]interface{}) (string, error)`:\n115:   - Base claims: `exp` = now+jwtExpiration (Unix), `iat` = now (Unix), `iss` = `\"agentcube-router\"`.\n116:   - Merges custom claims (e.g. `session_id`).\n117:   - Signing: `jwt.SigningMethodRS256`, signed with RSA private key.\n118: \n119: **Algorithm:** RS256  \n120: **Key type:** RSA 2048-bit, PKCS1 private key PEM (`RSA PRIVATE KEY`), PKIX public key PEM (`PUBLIC KEY`).\n121: \n122: **TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx):**\n123: \n124: - If `clientset == nil`, try `rest.InClusterConfig()`; on failure log warning and return nil (ephemeral keys).\n125: - Else build Secret `IdentitySecretName` in `IdentityNamespace`, type `Opaque`, labels `app=agentcube`, `component=router`, data `private.pem` + `public.pem`.\n126: - Create; on `AlreadyExists`, Get secret and `loadPrivateKeyPEM`.\n127: \n128: ### Reverse proxy\n129: \n130: - `httputil.NewSingleHostReverseProxy(targetURL)`; `proxy.Transport = s.httpTransport`.\n131: - Director: sets `req.URL.Path` to normalized path, clears `RawPath`, `req.Host = targetURL.Host`, forwarding headers, `Authorization` if JWT non-empty.\n132: - `ModifyResponse`: sets `x-agentcube-session-id`.\n133: - No per-request timeout wrapper (commented-out context timeout in source).\n134: \n135: ### Concurrency middleware\n136: \n137: - Buffered channel size `config.MaxConcurrentRequests`.\n138: - `select`: send to channel or `default` → 429 + abort.\n139: \n140: ### Health JSON shapes\n141: \n142: - Live: `{\"status\":\"alive\"}`.\n143: - Ready OK: `{\"status\":\"ready\"}`.\n144: - Ready fail: `{\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}`.\n145: \n146: ### Error helper (`handleGetSandboxError`)\n147: \n148: - If `apierrors.APIStatus`: use `Status().Code` if non-zero; message from status or `err.Error()`; if code is 500, replace message with `internal server error`; respond `gin.H{\"error\": message}`.\n149: - Else 500 `{\"error\":\"internal server error\"}`.\n150: \n151: ### Environment variables\n152: \n153: | Variable | Used by |\n154: |----------|---------|\n155: | `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` | Session manager (required) |\n156: | `AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE` | JWT secret namespace (optional, default `default`) |\n157: \n158: ### Dependencies (direct use in router)\n159: \n160: - `github.com/gin-gonic/gin`, `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5`, `golang.org/x/net/http2`, `k8s.io/api`, `k8s.io/apimachinery`, `k8s.io/client-go`, `k8s.io/klog/v2`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`, `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/api`.\n\n(End of file - total 160 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Session Routing — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- Same repository: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (see sandbox-orchestration design for `go.mod` and versions).\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router`\n\n### Config\n\n```go\nconst LastActivityAnnotationKey = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-activity\"\n\ntype Config struct {\n    Port                  string\n    Debug                 bool\n    EnableTLS             bool\n    TLSCert               string\n    TLSKey                string\n    MaxConcurrentRequests int  // 0 = unlimited at flag level; NewServer coerces to 1000","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md","time":{"start":1775826387484,"end":1775826387491}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775826388681,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d778042d0001BUAJ46CVav0yOj","messageID":"msg_d77802d2d001RjMbcTLsUTiF8B","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_02fef90dc1f24f9e946ea0c5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 agentcube 项目构建一个基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块（`pkg/router`），用于将外部 HTTP 请求路由到内部的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 服务实例。该模块将作为 agentcube 系统的流量入口，负责请求分发、负载均衡、服务发现和连接管理。\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In Scope\n10: \n11: 1. **核心反向代理引擎**\n12:    - 基于 `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` 构建可配置的反向代理\n13:    - 支持动态后端发现和路由规则更新\n14:    - 连接池管理和超时控制\n15: \n16: 2. **路由规则管理**\n17:    - 基于路径/Host 的路由匹配\n18:    - 支持通过 Kubernetes CRD（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）动态注册路由\n19:    - 路由优先级和冲突解决机制\n20: \n21: 3. **服务发现集成**\n22:    - 使用 `client-go` 的 Informer 机制监听 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n23:    - 利用 `SharedInformerFactory` 实现高效的事件驱动更新\n24:    - 通过 `Lister` 接口进行本地缓存查询，减少 API Server 压力\n25: \n26: 4. **负载均衡**\n27:    - 支持 Round-Robin、Least-Connections 等基础策略\n28:    - 健康检查与故障节点剔除\n29: \n30: 5. **中间件支持**\n31:    - 请求/响应日志\n32:    - 请求追踪（Trace ID 注入）\n33:    - 基础认证和限流\n34: \n35: ### Out of Scope\n36: \n37: - TLS 证书管理（由 Ingress Controller 处理）\n38: - 高级流量治理（灰度发布、A/B 测试）\n39: - WebSocket/gRPC 代理支持（后续迭代）\n40: \n41: ## Impact Analysis\n42: \n43: ### Dependencies\n44: \n45: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n46: |------|------|------|\n47: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | 访问 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD | 新增模块依赖，需确保 client-go 版本兼容 |\n48: | `k8s.io/client-go` | Informer/Lister 基础框架 | 间接依赖，版本需与 client-go 生成器一致（v0.34.1） |\n49: | `net/http` + `net/http/httputil` | 反向代理核心 | Go 标准库，无额外依赖 |\n50: \n51: ### Affected Components\n52: \n53: - **API Gateway/Ingress**: 本模块将作为其下游或直接替代部分功能\n54: - **AgentRuntime Controller**: 路由规则变更可能影响控制器的事件处理\n55: - **CodeInterpreter Service**: 新增的路由条目需要与现有服务端口配置对齐\n56: \n57: ### Risk Assessment\n58: \n59: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n60: |------|------|----------|\n61: | Informer 同步延迟导致路由不一致 | 中 | 设置合理的 `defaultResync`，实现降级到 API Server 直查 |\n62: | 后端服务不可用时的错误传播 | 中 | 实现断路器模式和重试机制 |\n63: | 高并发下的连接泄漏 | 低 | 使用 `http.Transport` 连接池配置，定期健康检查 |\n64: \n65: ## Alternatives Considered\n66: \n67: ### 1. 使用现有反向代理（Nginx/Envoy）\n68: \n69: **优点**: 功能成熟、社区支持好、配置丰富  \n70: **缺点**: 需要额外的运维负担、与 Kubernetes CRD 集成需要自定义 Controller、增加系统复杂度  \n71: **决策**: 不采用。agentcube 需要与 CRD 深度集成，自研 Go 模块可以更紧密地利用 client-go 的 Informer 机制。\n72: \n73: ### 2. 基于 Traefik/Contour 等云原生代理扩展\n74: \n75: **优点**: 原生支持 Kubernetes、CRD 路由定义  \n76: **缺点**: 学习曲线陡峭、自定义逻辑需要编写插件（通常为 Go 但受限于插件 API）、调试复杂  \n77: **决策**: 不采用。当前需求相对简单，自研可以更灵活地控制路由逻辑和与 agentcube 其他模块的交互。\n78: \n79: ### 3. 使用 Go 标准库 `httputil.ReverseProxy` 自研（选定方案）\n80: \n81: **优点**: \n82: - 与现有 `pkg/` 模块风格一致\n83: - 直接集成 client-go Informer/Lister 实现动态路由\n84: - 无额外运维负担，部署简单\n85: - 易于扩展和调试\n86: \n87: **缺点**: \n88: - 需要自行实现负载均衡和健康检查\n89: - 高级功能（如限流、熔断）需要额外开发\n90: \n91: **决策**: 采用。符合 agentcube 的技术栈和架构风格，M 规模的实现工作量可控。\n92: \n93: ## Implementation Notes\n94: \n95: ### 核心接口设计\n96: \n97: ```go\n98: type Router interface {\n99:     // AddRoute 动态添加路由规则\n100:     AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n101:     // RemoveRoute 移除路由规则\n102:     RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n103:     // ServeHTTP 实现 http.Handler 接口\n104:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n105: }\n106: \n107: type Backend struct {\n108:     URL      *url.URL\n109:     Weight   int\n110:     Healthy  bool\n111: }\n112: ```\n113: \n114: ### Informer 集成\n115: \n116: ```go\n117: // 使用 SharedInformerFactory 监听 CRD 变更\n118: factory := informers.NewSharedInformerFactory(clientset, 30*time.Second)\n119: agentRuntimeInformer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes()\n120: codeInterpreterInformer := factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters()\n121: \n122: // 注册事件处理器\n123: agentRuntimeInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n124:     AddFunc:    onAgentRuntimeAdded,\n125:     UpdateFunc: onAgentRuntimeUpdated,\n126:     DeleteFunc: onAgentRuntimeDeleted,\n127: })\n128: ```\n129: \n130: ### 目录结构\n131: \n132: ```\n133: pkg/router/\n134: ├── router.go          # Router 接口和核心实现\n135: ├── proxy.go           # ReverseProxy 封装\n136: ├── backend.go         # Backend 管理和健康检查\n137: ├── loadbalancer.go    # 负载均衡策略\n138: ├── middleware.go      # 中间件（日志、追踪、限流）\n139: ├── informer.go        # CRD Informer 集成\n140: ├── config.go          # 配置结构体\n141: └── router_test.go     # 单元测试\n142: ```\n\n(End of file - total 142 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 agentcube 项目构建一个基于 Go 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块（`pkg/router`），用于将外部 HTTP 请求路由到内部的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 服务实例。该模块将作为 agentcube 系统的流量入口，负责请求分发、负载均衡、服务发现和连接管理。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **核心反向代理引擎**\n   - 基于 `net/http/httputil.ReverseProxy` 构建可配置的反向代理\n   - 支持动态后端发现和路由规则更新\n   - 连接池管理和超时控制\n\n2. **路由规则管理**\n   - 基于路径/Host 的路由匹配\n   - 支持通过 Kubernetes CRD（AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter）动态注册路由\n   - 路由优先级和冲突解决机制\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775826388674,"end":1775826388679}}}}
