{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775826397559,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d77806975001JrhAMAz0cQCewP","messageID":"msg_d778062db001Qvyg3eSSZ9X18S","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775826473779,"sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","part":{"id":"prt_d7780731d001LsYdO8RtQSTYdx","messageID":"msg_d778062db001Qvyg3eSSZ9X18S","sessionID":"ses_288822a77ffew8zG4LGC9Q7q95","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_75be69ac697a492cb24f429e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`pkg/router` 是 AgentCube 系统的流量入口，负责将外部 HTTP 请求反向代理到 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 sandbox pod。核心职责：\n\n1. **Session 解析与 Sandbox 创建**：通过 session ID 从 store 查找 sandbox，或在 session ID 为空时通过 WorkloadManager 创建新 sandbox\n2. **HTTP 反向代理**：将请求代理到 sandbox 的 entry point，注入 RS256 JWT 签名\n3. **动态服务发现**：通过 client-go Informer 监听 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n4. **流量治理**：负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/router/\n├── config.go              # Config 结构体与默认值\n├── server.go              # Server 结构体、构造函数、启动/关闭\n├── session_manager.go     # SessionManager 接口与实现\n├── jwt.go                 # JWTManager、密钥管理、token 生成\n├── proxy.go               # ReverseProxy 封装、Director、ErrorHandler\n├── backend.go             # Backend 管理、健康检查\n├── loadbalancer.go        # Round-Robin、Least-Connections 负载均衡\n├── middleware.go          # 并发限制、日志、Trace ID 中间件\n├── informer.go            # CRD Informer 集成、事件处理\n├── router.go              # Router 接口、路由表管理\n├── errors.go              # 自定义错误类型\n└── *_test.go              # 单元测试\n\ncmd/router/\n└── main.go                # CLI 入口、标志解析\n```\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系\n\n```\npkg/router\n├── github.com/gin-gonic/gin              # HTTP 路由引擎\n├── github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5          # RS256 JWT 签名\n├── golang.org/x/net/http2                # HTTP/2 支持\n├── k8s.io/api                            # K8s API 类型\n├── k8s.io/apimachinery                   # errors, schema, runtime\n├── k8s.io/client-go                      # rest, kubernetes.Interface\n├── k8s.io/klog/v2                        # 结构化日志\n├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go        # 生成的 typed client\n├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1  # CRD 类型\n├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types           # 共享类型（Kind, SandboxInfo）\n├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store                  # Session store 接口\n└── net/http/httputil                     # Go 标准库反向代理\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构\n\n### 2.1 Config\n\n```go\ntype Config struct {\n    Port                  string // 监听端口，默认 \"8080\"\n    Debug                 bool   // Gin debug 模式\n    EnableTLS             bool   // 是否启用 TLS\n    TLSCert               string // TLS 证书路径\n    TLSKey                string // TLS 私钥路径\n    MaxConcurrentRequests int    // 最大并发请求数，默认 1000\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 Server\n\n```go\ntype Server struct {\n    config         *Config\n    engine         *gin.Engine\n    httpServer     *http.Server\n    sessionManager SessionManager\n    storeClient    store.Store\n    httpTransport  *http.Transport\n    jwtManager     *JWTManager\n}\n```\n\n- `httpTransport`: `IdleConnTimeout: 0`（不回收空闲连接），`DisableCompression: false`\n- `httpServer`: `ReadTimeout: 30s`, `IdleTimeout: 90s`, 支持 h2c 明文升级\n\n### 2.3 SessionManager\n\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n\ntype manager struct {\n    storeClient     store.Store\n    workloadMgrAddr string\n    httpClient      *http.Client\n}\n```\n\n- `httpClient.Timeout`: 2 分钟\n- Transport: `MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`, `DisableCompression: false`, HTTP/2 `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`, `PingTimeout: 15s`\n\n### 2.4 JWTManager\n\n```go\nconst (\n    rsaKeySize         = 2048\n    jwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n    IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n    PrivateKeyDataKey  = \"private.pem\"\n    PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n)\n\nvar IdentityNamespace = \"default\" // init(): AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 覆盖\n\ntype JWTManager struct {\n    privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n    publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n    clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n}\n```\n\n- `NewJWTManager()`: 生成 RSA 2048-bit 密钥对\n- `GenerateToken(claims)`: RS256 签名，基础 claims `exp`, `iat`, `iss=\"agentcube-router\"`\n- `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)`: 创建或加载 K8s Secret 中的密钥对\n\n### 2.5 Router 与 Backend\n\n```go\ntype Router interface {\n    AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n    RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n    ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n}\n\ntype Backend struct {\n    URL      *url.URL\n    Weight   int\n    Healthy  bool\n}\n\ntype routerImpl struct {\n    mu       sync.RWMutex\n    routes   map[string]Backend\n    lb       LoadBalancer\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 LoadBalancer\n\n```go\ntype LoadBalancer interface {\n    Select(backends []Backend) (*Backend, error)\n}\n\ntype RoundRobinBalancer struct {\n    mu      sync.Mutex\n    current int\n}\n\ntype LeastConnectionsBalancer struct {\n    connections map[string]*atomic.Int64\n}\n```\n\n### 2.7 BackendHealthChecker\n\n```go\ntype BackendHealthChecker struct {\n    interval          time.Duration // 默认 30s\n    consecutiveFail   int           // 标记不健康阈值，默认 3\n    consecutiveSuccess int          // 标记健康阈值，默认 2\n    checker           func(*url.URL) (bool, error)\n}\n```\n\n### 2.8 自定义错误类型\n\n```go\ntype SessionNotFoundError struct {\n    SessionID string\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplateNotFoundError struct {\n    Namespace string\n    Name      string\n    Kind      string\n}\n\nfunc (e *SessionNotFoundError) Error() string\nfunc (e *SandboxTemplateNotFoundError) Error() string\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. API 契约\n\n### 3.1 路由注册\n\n| Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n|--------|------|------------|---------|\n| GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n| GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n| GET, POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n| GET, POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n\n### 3.2 Health 端点响应\n\n**Liveness:**\n```json\nGET /health/live → 200 {\"status\":\"alive\"}\n```\n\n**Readiness:**\n```json\nGET /health/ready → 200 {\"status\":\"ready\"}\nGET /health/ready → 503 {\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}\n```\n\n### 3.3 反向代理行为\n\n**Upstream URL 确定：**\n1. 从 `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 查找第一个 `path` 前缀匹配 invocation path 的 entry point\n2. 无匹配时使用第一个 entry point\n3. EntryPoints 为空时返回 404 `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n\n**Director 设置：**\n- `req.URL.Path`: 规范化路径（Gin `*path` 无前导 `/` 时自动添加）\n- `req.URL.RawPath`: 清空\n- `req.Host`: `targetURL.Host`\n- `X-Forwarded-Host`: 原始请求 `Host`\n- `X-Forwarded-Proto`: `\"https\"`（TLS 存在）或 `\"http\"`\n- `X-Forwarded-For`: 追加客户端 IP\n- `Authorization`: `Bearer <JWT>`（仅 `Sandbox`/`SandboxClaim` kind）\n\n**ModifyResponse:**\n- 设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID\n\n### 3.4 JWT 注入\n\n对 `Sandbox` 和 `SandboxClaim` kind 的 sandbox：\n- 代理前生成 JWT token\n- 设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 到代理请求\n- JWT 签名失败时返回 500 `{\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\",\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"}`\n\n### 3.5 代理错误映射\n\n| 错误信息 | HTTP 状态码 | 响应体 |\n|----------|-------------|--------|\n| 包含 `\"connection refused\"` | 502 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}` |\n| 包含 `\"timeout\"` | 504 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}` |\n| 其他错误 | 502 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}` |\n\n### 3.6 并发限制中间件\n\n- 基于 buffered channel 的信号量，容量 `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n- 槽位耗尽时返回 429 `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}`\n- 仅应用于 `/v1` 路由组，health 端点不受限制\n\n### 3.7 Last-activity 更新\n\n- sandbox 解析成功后调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, time.Now())`\n- `forwardToSandbox` 返回后再次调用\n- 失败仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程\n\n---\n\n## 4. 错误处理\n\n### 4.1 错误分类\n\n| 错误类型 | 来源 | 处理方式 |\n|----------|------|----------|\n| `SessionNotFoundError` | Store 中不存在 session | 404 JSON |\n| `SandboxTemplateNotFoundError` | WorkloadManager 返回非 200 | 404 JSON |\n| JWT 签名失败 | `GenerateToken` 返回错误 | 500 JSON `JWT_SIGNING_FAILED` |\n| 连接拒绝 | 反向代理 ErrorHandler | 502 `sandbox unreachable` |\n| 超时 | 反向代理 ErrorHandler | 504 `sandbox timeout` |\n| 并发超限 | `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | 429 `SERVER_OVERLOADED` |\n| K8s API 错误 | `apierrors.APIStatus` | 使用 status code，500 时替换消息为 `internal server error` |\n\n### 4.2 错误辅助函数\n\n```go\nfunc handleGetSandboxError(c *gin.Context, err error) {\n    if statusErr, ok := err.(apierrors.APIStatus); ok {\n        code := statusErr.Status().Code\n        if code == 0 {\n            code = http.StatusInternalServerError\n        }\n        message := statusErr.Status().Message\n        if message == \"\" {\n            message = err.Error()\n        }\n        if code == http.StatusInternalServerError {\n            message = \"internal server error\"\n        }\n        c.JSON(int(code), gin.H{\"error\": message})\n        return\n    }\n    c.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{\"error\": \"internal server error\"})\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 日志策略\n\n- 使用 `slog` 或 `klog`，禁止 `log.Printf`\n- 结构化日志字段：`method`, `path`, `status`, `duration_ms`, `trace_id`\n- 警告级别：store 更新失败、service account token 读取失败（非 NotExist）、非 in-cluster JWT 密钥初始化\n\n---\n\n## 5. 测试策略\n\n### 5.1 单元测试覆盖\n\n| 文件 | 测试内容 |\n|------|----------|\n| `config_test.go` | 默认值、CLI 标志解析、`MaxConcurrentRequests <= 0` 时 NewServer 设为 1000 |\n| `server_test.go` | Debug/Release 模式、JWT 初始化失败、`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置、TLS 配置验证 |\n| `session_manager_test.go` | session 查找、session 创建、Store NotFound、WorkloadManager 非 200、token 附加 |\n| `jwt_test.go` | token 生成、claims 验证、RS256 算法、Secret 创建/加载、ephemeral keys 路径 |\n| `proxy_test.go` | Director 设置、ModifyResponse、upstream URL 确定、协议拼接、path 规范化 |\n| `backend_test.go` | 健康检查成功/失败、连续失败阈值、单次失败不立即标记 |\n| `loadbalancer_test.go` | Round-Robin 循环、跳过不健康、Least-Connections 选择、全不健康错误 |\n| `middleware_test.go` | 并发限制通过/拒绝、槽位释放、health 端点不受限、Trace ID 注入 |\n| `router_test.go` | 路由添加/删除/重复/幂等、并发安全、ServeHTTP 匹配/404 |\n| `informer_test.go` | CRD 事件处理、路由表更新、Lister 缓存查询 |\n\n### 5.2 并发测试\n\n```bash\ngo test -race ./pkg/router/...\n```\n\n覆盖场景：\n- 并发 `AddRoute`/`RemoveRoute`\n- 并发负载均衡选择\n- 并发健康检查状态更新\n- 并发中间件槽位获取/释放\n\n### 5.3 门禁要求\n\n1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n2. `go build ./cmd/router/...` 编译通过\n3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n4. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n5. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（`grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/` 无匹配）\n\n### 5.4 Mock 策略\n\n- `store.Store`: 使用接口 mock 实现 NotFound/成功场景\n- `kubernetes.Interface`: 使用 `client-go` fake clientset\n- WorkloadManager HTTP: 使用 `httptest.NewServer`\n- Informer: 使用 fake clientset + 手动触发事件\n\n---\n\n## 6. 实现步骤\n\n### Phase 1: 基础结构（Day 1-2）\n\n1. 创建 `pkg/router/config.go` — Config 结构体与默认值\n2. 创建 `pkg/router/errors.go` — 自定义错误类型\n3. 创建 `pkg/router/jwt.go` — JWTManager、密钥管理\n4. 创建 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` — SessionManager 接口与实现\n5. 编写对应单元测试\n\n### Phase 2: 反向代理核心（Day 3-4）\n\n1. 创建 `pkg/router/proxy.go` — ReverseProxy 封装、Director、ErrorHandler\n2. 创建 `pkg/router/backend.go` — Backend 管理、健康检查\n3. 创建 `pkg/router/loadbalancer.go` — Round-Robin、Least-Connections\n4. 创建 `pkg/router/middleware.go` — 并发限制、日志、Trace ID\n5. 编写对应单元测试\n\n### Phase 3: 路由与服务器（Day 5-6）\n\n1. 创建 `pkg/router/router.go` — Router 接口、路由表管理\n2. 创建 `pkg/router/informer.go` — CRD Informer 集成、事件处理\n3. 创建 `pkg/router/server.go` — Server 结构体、构造函数、路由注册、Start/Stop\n4. 创建 `cmd/router/main.go` — CLI 入口、标志解析\n5. 编写集成测试\n\n### Phase 4: 集成与门禁（Day 7）\n\n1. 运行 `go build ./pkg/router/... ./cmd/router/...`\n2. 运行 `go test ./pkg/router/... -v`\n3. 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/router/...`\n4. 检查 `log.Printf` 残留\n5. 修复所有问题，确保门禁通过\n\n---\n\n## 7. 后续变更\n\n| 变更 | 描述 | 优先级 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| AR-010 | 高级流量治理（灰度发布、A/B 测试） | P1 |\n| AR-011 | WebSocket/gRPC 代理支持 | P2 |\n| AR-012 | 基于 Prometheus 的动态负载均衡 | P2 |\n| AR-013 | 分布式追踪集成（OpenTelemetry） | P3 |\n| AR-014 | TLS 证书自动轮转 | P3 |\n\n### 已知限制\n\n- 当前不支持 per-backend 超时配置（使用全局 `http.Transport`）\n- 健康检查路径固定为 `/health`，后续可配置化\n- 负载均衡策略仅支持 Round-Robin 和 Least-Connections，后续可扩展 Weighted Round-Robin\n- JWT 密钥固定 RS256，后续可支持 ES256 等其他算法\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime.go\">\nERROR [51:25] undefined: LabelSessionID\nERROR [77:29] undefined: LabelSandboxName\nERROR [78:29] undefined: LabelWorkloadName\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/codeinterpreter.go\">\nERROR [11:2] \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\" imported as metav1 and not used\nERROR [32:25] undefined: LabelSessionID\nERROR [58:29] undefined: LabelSandboxName\nERROR [59:29] undefined: LabelWorkloadName\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/event_handlers.go\">\nERROR [105:28] undefined: LabelSandboxName\nERROR [130:31] undefined: LabelSandboxName\nERROR [164:103] undefined: LabelSandboxName\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/pod.go\">\nERROR [31:28] undefined: LabelSandboxName\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go\">\nERROR [78:24] cannot use (func() li